# Metrics
- Create success/failure counts; resolve latency histogram; cache hit ratio.
- Rate-limit throttle counts; webhook delivery results.

# SLOs
- Resolve p95 < 25ms from cache, < 150ms fallback DB (intra-region).
- 99.9% monthly availability for resolve endpoint.

# Tracing
- Trace ID on every request; propagate to async jobs.

